snippet.title: Malice & Greed | Gameplay Clip
snippet.description:
Malice & Greed is a roguelite RPG where you force enemies to join you, and steal their skills! Available now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1566090/Malice__Greed/

The Reawakening update is now live: https://steamcommunity.com/app/1566090/eventcomments/5503948370866739258?snr=1_2108_9__2107

Music: Torn to Shreds - Valeriy Baryshev (Malice & Greed OST, 2021)
